Put the spray bottle in the bottom right cabinet

Grab the spray bottle off of the counter
Back up and face the cabinets below the sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the tub, then hang a left and walk up to the small silver bin to the left of the counter.
Pick up the white spray bottle out of the silver bin.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk towards the tub, turn left again to face the counter.
Open the right drawer below the counter and put the white spray bottle inside, then close the drawer.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the white spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and take a step forward, turn left again to face the counter.
Open the right drawer below the counter and put the white spray bottle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two white spray bottles into a drawer.
